        "translation": "Here, then, is the one.",
        "source": "X69n1339_001:0197b07_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故我琅邪禪師之出化也。",
        "translation": "That's why I, Luang Xie Chanshi, have been transformed since my teacher's appearance.",
